labels.value: Verify That You Will Be Able To Save A Previously Placed Order As A PDF File

name: Validate_That_You_Will_Be_Able_To_Save_Previously_Placed_Order_As_A_Pdf_File
description:
Test Steps:

1- Goto http://live.techpanda.org/
2- Click On My Account Link
3- Login In Application Using Previously Created Credential
4- Click On 'My Orders'
5- Click On 'View Order'
6- Verify The Previously Created Order Is Displayed In 'Recent Orders' Table And Status Is Pending
7- Click On 'Print Order' Link
8- Verify Order Is Saved As Pdf.

Expected Result:

- Previously Created Order Is Displayed In 'Recent Orders' Table And Status Is Pending
- Order Is Saved As Pdf file.

Actual Result:

- Previously Created Order Is Displayed In 'Recent Orders' Successfully 
- Order Is Saved As Pdf file Successfully.

Priority:

- Medium
